data.description: Gigantic well maintained obviously well-loved 4 bedroom expanded brick "generational living" bungalow with fully finished basement, baths on all levels, 3-1/2 car brick garage. Sunny and bright large and light spacious kitchen with a gas stove, white refrigerator and built-in dishwasher!  Riverside school systems! 96 and 208. Impressive well maintained solid brick family home that has enough room for extended family living. Corner lot with a large  brick patio between the house and 3-1/2 car brick garage. This home has the rare feature of an underground sprinkler system so the lawn is always lush and green. So close the the Village Commons you can hear the summer concerts from your own back yard. Gleaming golden oak hardwood floor, cozy and warmth emitting gas fireplace in the combined living/dining rooms; 3 1st floor bedrooms, in-law suite or master en suite on the second floor and still storage galore throughout this residence. The gigantic basement has a recreational area and a former beauty shop set up. Half bath too. This is one you need to see! Transferred in 100% As-Is condition. All viillage code requirements have been done!!  Unload the moving truck and start loving your new home!
